E_{\mathrm{c}} &= m_{\mathrm{p}} + E_{\mathrm{c}}^{\mathrm{th}} = m_{\mathrm{p}} + \frac{M}{2} = 0.94 + \frac{90}{2} = 45.94\ \mathrm{(GeV)}
\end{aligned}
\]

共振峰的截面为
$$
\sigma = \frac{2 J + 1}{\left(2 J_{\mathrm{p}} + 1\right) \left(2 J_{\overline{\mathrm{p}}} + 1\right)} \pi \lambda^{2} \frac{\Gamma_{\mathrm{p}} \Gamma}{(E - M)^{2} + \frac{\Gamma^{2}}{4}}
$$
当 $E = M$, 发生共振，假设共振态的自旋为 $J = 0$，而 $J_{\mathrm{p}} = 1/2$，
$$
\sigma(J = 0) = \pi \lambda^{2} \frac{\Gamma_{\mathrm{p}}}{\Gamma}
$$
由题设 $\frac{\Gamma_{\mathrm{p} \overline{\mathrm{p}}}}{\Gamma} = 0.1, \, \lambda = \frac{\hbar}{p}$，所以
$$
\begin{aligned}
\sigma & = \pi \lambda^{2} \frac{\Gamma_{\mathrm{p} \overline{\mathrm{p}}}}{\Gamma} = \pi \left(\frac{\hbar c}{p c}\right)^{2} \times 0.1 = \pi \times \left(\frac{197 \times 10^{-13}}{3740}\right)^{2} \times 0.1 \\
& = 8.7 \times 10^{-30} \, \mathrm{cm}^{2} = 8.7 \, \mu\mathrm{b}
\end{aligned}
$$

为了得到反应 $\mathrm{e}+\gamma \rightarrow \mu$ 的阈频率 $\omega_{0}$，在质心系中，总能量必须等于 $M$，洛伦兹不变量

$$
\begin{gathered}
-M^{2} = \left(p_{\mathrm{e}}+p_{\gamma}\right)^{2} \\
\left(\omega_{0}+m\right)^{2} - \omega_{0}^{2} = M^{2}
\end{gathered}
$$

由此得到

$$
\omega_{0} = \frac{M^{2}-m^{2}}{2m}
$$

