原子从 $A \rightarrow B$ 的衰变率为

\[
\lambda_{1} = \frac{0.1}{\tau}
\]

于是

\[
4 \pi I = \frac{n h c \lambda_{1}}{\lambda_{\mathrm{B}}}
\]

其中 $I$ 为所求的光强度，已知 $\lambda_{B} = 500 \, \mathrm{nm}$ ，为 $\mathrm{A} \rightarrow \mathrm{B}$ 的跃迁辐射波长，故

\[
\begin{aligned}
I & = \frac{n h c}{40 \pi \tau \lambda_{\mathrm{B}}} = \frac{1.4 \times 10^{5} \times 6.63 \times 10^{-27} \times 10^{10}}{40 \times 3.14 \times 2 \times 10^{-8} \times 500 \times 10^{-7}} \\
& = 0.22 \, \mathrm{erg}/(\mathrm{s} \cdot \mathrm{sr}) = 2.2 \times 10^{-8} \, \mathrm{W}/\mathrm{sr}
\end{aligned}
\]

令 \(\frac{\mathrm{d}W}{\mathrm{d}\Omega^{*}}\) 和 \(\frac{\mathrm{d}W}{\mathrm{d}\Omega}\) 分别代表在质心系和实验室系单位立体角产生 \(\pi^{+}\) 的归一化概率。带 * 的量表示质心系的量，由题得知

\[
\begin{aligned}
& \frac{\mathrm{d}W}{\mathrm{d}\Omega^{*}} = \frac{1}{4\pi} \\
& \frac{\mathrm{d}W}{\mathrm{d}\Omega} = \frac{\mathrm{d}W}{\mathrm{d}\Omega^{*}} \frac{\mathrm{d}\Omega^{*}}{\mathrm{d}\Omega} = \frac{1}{4\pi} \frac{\mathrm{d}\cos\theta^{*}}{\mathrm{d}\cos\theta}
\end{aligned}
\]

对所产生的 \(\pi\) 的动量能量作罗伦兹变换

\[
\begin{align*}
p^{*} \sin\theta^{*} &= p \sin\theta  \tag{1}\\
p^{*} \cos\theta^{*} &= \gamma'\left(p \cos\theta - \beta' E\right)  \tag{2}\\
E^{*} &= \gamma'\left(E - \beta' p \cos\theta\right) \tag{3}
\end{align*}
\]

其中 \(\gamma'\), \(\beta'\) 分别为质心在实验室系中的洛伦兹因子和速度。将 (2) 式对 \(\cos\theta\) 微分并注意到 \(p^{*}\), \(E^{*}\) 与 \(\theta\) 无关，得

\[
p^{*} \frac{\mathrm{d}\cos\theta^{*}}{\mathrm{d} \cos\theta} = \gamma'\left(p + \cos\theta \frac{\mathrm{d}p}{\mathrm{d}\cos\theta} - \beta' \frac{\mathrm{d}E}{\mathrm{d}p} \frac{\mathrm{d}p}{\mathrm{d}\cos\theta}\right)
\]

已知 \(E = (m^{2}c^{4} + p^{2}c^{2})^{1/2}, \frac{\mathrm{d}E}{\mathrm{d}p} = \frac{pc^{2}}{E} = \beta c\)，从而得到

\[
p^{*} \frac{\mathrm{d}\cos\theta^{*}}{\mathrm{d} \cos\theta} = \gamma'\left(p + \cos\theta \frac{\mathrm{d}p}{\mathrm{d}\cos\theta} - \beta'\beta c \frac{\mathrm{d}p}{\mathrm{d}\cos\theta}\right) \tag{4}
\]

将(3)式对 \(\cos\theta\) 微分并注意到 \(p^{*}\), \(E^{*}\) 与 \(\theta\) 无关，得

\[
\begin{aligned}
0 &= \gamma'\left(\frac{\mathrm{d}E}{\mathrm{d} \cos\theta} - \beta' p c - \beta' \cos\theta \frac{\mathrm{d}p}{\mathrm{d} \cos\theta}\right) \\
&= \gamma'\left(\beta c \frac{\mathrm{d}p}{\mathrm{d} \cos\theta} - \beta' p c - \beta' \cos\theta \frac{\mathrm{d}p}{\mathrm{d} \cos\theta}\right)
\end{aligned}
\]

因此

\[
\frac{\mathrm{d}p}{\mathrm{d} \cos\theta} = \frac{p\beta' c}{\beta c - \beta' \cos\theta} \tag{5}
\]

把(5)式代入(4)式得到

\[
\begin{aligned}
p^{*} \frac{\mathrm{d}\cos\theta^{*}}{\mathrm{d} \cos\theta} &= \gamma'\left(p + \frac{\left(\cos\theta - \beta'\beta\right) \beta' p}{\beta c - \beta' \cos\theta}\right) \\
&= \frac{\left(1 - \beta'^{2}\right) \gamma' \beta p}{\beta c - \beta' \cos\theta} \\
&= \frac{p}{\gamma'\left[1 - \left(\beta' \cos\theta\right) / \beta\right]}
\end{aligned}
\]

所以在实验室系产生 \(\pi\) 的立体角分布为

\[
\begin{aligned}
\frac{\mathrm{d}W}{\mathrm{d}\Omega} &= \frac{1}{4\pi} \frac{\mathrm{d}\cos\theta^{*}}{\mathrm{d} \cos\theta} \\
&= \frac{p}{4\pi \gamma' p^{*}\left[1 - \left(\beta' \cos\theta\right) / \beta\right]} \\
&= \frac{m_{\pi} \beta}{4\pi \gamma' p^{*}\left[1 - \left(\beta' \cos\theta\right) / \beta\right]}
\end{aligned}
\]

